<HEAD>Current Quotations</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   ``We need to end the needless sacrifices of men, women and
children on the altar of congressional inaction. ... Congress has
acquiesced to the gun lobby. The only thing that will bring an end
to this inaction is an aroused citizenry.'' _ Coretta Scott King,
widow of slain civil rights leader Martin Luther King Jr., urging
lawmakers to restrict sales of handguns.
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
   ``I have been to his classroom. I have seen the miracle in
process. Jaime Escalante is dedicated to his students, he is
dedicated to their future. He is a true, genuine American hero.'' _
Secretary of Education William J. Bennett, praising the East Los
Angeles teacher whose success in teaching calculus to Hispanic
teen-agers was featured in the movie ``Stand and Deliver.''
</TEXT>
